column5: Anyone hear about the bite as of late. Are the big Girls in now.
Not yet Not much going on here yet I don't know what is going on, last year at this time was great I'm sure it will get better Hopefully before November

Lots of small walleye and the guys who are putting there time in on the river have been getting at least 1 28 inch plus fish in there 2-3 days here. The unstabble weathers not doing us any favors but the Pike fishing in the river has been great for over a week now. Steve
Any room in the Vanity Cup this year ?? finally have sometime to fish this fall , maybe just have to go the week before and try it out.Thanks
Full. Best thing to do is get your name on the wait list (long) and make sure it stays there. Eventually youll get in. Steve
